    <div class="tab-content">
    <dl><dd><ol><li><p> [perish;die out]∶消失;灭亡</p></li><li><p> [annihilate;eliminate;exterminate;wipe out]∶使消灭;除掉[敌对的或有害的]人或事物</p></li></ol></dd></dl>
